{
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "lines": [
        "Routes audio from the",
        "mic/line-in jack through",
        "Move Everything's chain.",
        "",
        "Supports Line, Guitar,",
        "and Phono input types",
        "with dedicated signal",
        "conditioning for each."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Input Types",
      "lines": [
        "Line: Balanced input",
        " for synths, mixers.",
        "",
        "Guitar: Hi-Z input",
        " for guitars, basses.",
        "",
        "Phono: RIAA EQ for",
        " turntables/vinyl."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Signal Conditioning",
      "lines": [
        "Input/Output Trim",
        "Noise Gate (threshold,",
        " attack, hold, release)",
        "High-pass filter",
        "Safety limiter",
        "Cable compensation",
        "Soft clip",
        "Hum notch (50/60 Hz)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Feedback Warning",
      "lines": [
        "When no cable is in the",
        "mic/line-in jack, the",
        "internal microphone may",
        "be active. This creates",
        "a feedback loop: mic ->",
        "Line In -> speaker ->",
        "mic.",
        "",
        "If Feedback Guard is on",
        "(Settings > Safety),",
        "audio is gated until",
        "you dismiss the warning.",
        "",
        "Plug in a cable to",
        "disable the internal",
        "mic and avoid feedback."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
